name: Openstreetmap, Great Britain Railways,Great Britain, 2008
description: This data was provided by Openstreetmaps and shows the locations of the Railway infrastructure in Great Britain, which includes England, Wales and Scotland. Railways include trams, subways, and standard trains. This railway data set was uploaded as a poly line shape file and includes attribute information for Feature name and feature type.
